= Introduction
<introduction>
The resolution of the black hole information paradox remains a profound
challenge in theoretical physics @hawking1976. Recent developments in
AdS/CFT correspondence suggest unitary evolution is preserved.

= Holographic Entanglement Entropy
<holographic-entanglement-entropy>
The Ryu-Takayanagi formula relates the entanglement entropy #mi(`S_A`)
to the area of a minimal surface #mi(`\gamma_A`):
$ #mitex(`\begin{equation}
S_A = \frac{\text{Area}(\gamma_A)}{4G_N}
\end{equation}`) $

